UMtshali (87), owake waklonyeliswa nge- Order of Mendi for Bravery in Silver, ushonele esibhedlela iNkosi Albert Luthuli Hospital eThekwini izolo ngemuva kokugula obesekumxine isikhathi eside. Leli qhawe lazalelwa eClermont, eThekwini, futhi lajoyina umzabalazo ngemuva kokuphothula isikole. Wayeyisishoshovu samalungelo abasebenzi, isosha loMkhonto weSizwe (MK) ngaphambi kokuba yilungu lePhalamende ngo-1994. Wayeqeqeshelwe ezempi nobunhloli eRussia naseCuba. Ngo-2014 uMtshali wahlonishwa ngokuthi kuqanjwe isikole samabanga aphezulu eWyebank ngegama lakhe. -ANA